        children (
            {
                id w8-stack
                title "Tier 1: network stack → Session.stack. Create Session; move MAIN_STACK/ARENA in; stack_* wrappers take &mut Session; thread &mut Session through dispatch, ~100 iface_* fns, bins, and iface tests. Remove the stack thread_locals."
                priority 0
                log (
